msgctxt "72_Employee"
msgid "Good to see you, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Bienvenido, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "84_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey there. I'm here looking for a nice new dress for this girl here. Think you could help me pick something out for her?"
msgstr "Ah, hola. Vine a comprarle ropa a esta mujer.\n"\n"¿Podrías ayudarme a elegir algo que le quede bien?"

msgctxt "96_Employee"
msgid "Of course, sir. Let's see... What do you think of these?"
msgstr "¿En serio? Veamos... ¿qué te parece este conjunto?"

msgctxt "120_Akiyama"
msgid "(No, I've got to buy it here.)"
msgstr "(No, tenemos que comprar aquí sí o sí)."

msgctxt "132_Employee"
msgid "Thank you very much. That dress is absolutely perfect for you, if you don't mind me saying!"
msgstr "Gracias. Creo que es un vestido que le queda muy bien."

msgctxt "144_Employee"
msgid "Thank you very much. That dress is absolutely perfect for you, if you don't mind me saying!"
msgstr "Gracias. Creo que es un vestido que le queda muy bien."

msgctxt "156_Akiyama"
msgid "You can send the bill over to my secretary Hana-chan. Sorry for the trouble."
msgstr "Perdón, pero... ¿podrías cobrarle a Hana-chan de mi parte?"

msgctxt "168_Employee"
msgid "It's no trouble at all, sir! We'll do just that. Please come again soon."
msgstr "Entendido. Espero verlos de nuevo pronto."

msgctxt "180_Employee"
msgid "Welcome."
msgstr "Bienvenido."

msgctxt "204_Employee"
msgid "Thank you very much."
msgstr "Muchas gracias."

